<div class="card !bg-navy-50 !border-navy-100 space-y-4">
  <h2 class="font-semibold text-navy-900">How to get a key</h2>

  <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm text-navy-700">
    <li class="flex gap-3">
      <span class="badge-info shrink-0">1</span>
      <span>
        Create an account at
        <%= link_to "console.anthropic.com", "https://console.anthropic.com", target: "_blank", rel: "noopener", class: "font-medium text-navy-900 underline" %>
        — this is the developer console, not the claude.ai chat app.
      </span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex gap-3">
      <span class="badge-info shrink-0">2</span>
      <span>Go to <strong>Settings → Billing</strong> and add a payment method. $5–10 in credits is plenty to start.</span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex gap-3">
      <span class="badge-info shrink-0">3</span>
      <span>Go to <strong>Settings → API Keys → Create Key</strong>, then copy the key — it starts with <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">sk-ant-...</code> and is only shown once.</span>
    </li>
    <li class="flex gap-3">
      <span class="badge-info shrink-0">4</span>
      <span>Paste it below and save.</span>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <div class="border-t border-navy-200 pt-4">
    <p class="text-sm text-navy-700">
      <strong>What this costs:</strong> there's no subscription or free tier —
      you pay only for what you use. For normal use (a plan update every
      couple of weeks, daily activity reactions, occasional chat) that's
      roughly <strong>$2–4/month</strong>. You can set a monthly spend limit
      under <strong>Settings → Limits</strong> on the Anthropic Console so you're
      never surprised.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
